Adeniran Ogunsanya Street bụ okporo ámá dị na mpaghara gọọmentị mpaghara Surulere nke Lagos Steeti ma dị n'akụkụ Akangba
A na-akpọ ya aha Adeniran Ogunsanya.
Okporo ámá Adeniran Ogunsanya bụ ebe a ma ama Adeniran Оgunsanya Shopping Mall.
Adeniran Ogunsanya Shopping Mall nke a makwara dị ka Leisure Mall bụ ụlọ ahịa ahịa ultramodern dị na Adeniran Оgunsanya Striti
Gọvanọ ndị agha nke Lagos Steeti n'oge ahụ, Brigadier-General Mobolaji Johnson wuru ma nye ya iwu na 1975, gọọmentị Babatunde Fashola mechara rụzigharịa ụlọ ahịa ahụ na afọ 2011
Tupu mmezigharị ya na afo 2011, a maara ya dị ka "Adeniran Ogunsanya Shopping Centre" n'okpuru njikwa LSDPC (Lagos State Development and Property Corporation)
N'oge a, ọ nwere ọtụtụ azụmaahịa dị ka "Ices Parlour" (ụlọ ahịa na-ere ihe nracha) "Jack na Judy" (uwe ejiji ụlọ akwụkwọ) ụlọ ahịa akwụkwọ Patabah, na "Omo Onikoyi" (ụlọ ntutu isi)
Ọ nwere ugbu a ngụkọta nke ihe dị ka square mita 22,000 na ihe karịrị ụlọ ahịa 150, ngwugwu ụgbọ ala nke nwere ike ịnwe ihe karịrị ụgbọala 300, elevator, escalator na ihe ndị ọzọ dị mkpa.
